ContentDesc_Chrysalis: A ruthless Ascian known as Nabriales has intruded upon the sanctum of the Scions of the Seventh Dawn, spiriting away both the Antecedent and the powerful relic she refused to yield. Pursue the Paragon through the dimensional rift and prise Minfilia─and Tupsimati─from his tenebrous grasp.
Instancecontenttextdata_7800_Text: I shall not toy with you as does Lahabrea!Witness the terrible might of a true servant of Zodiark!
Instancecontenttextdata_7801_Text: Writhing powers of ruination!From the deepest pits of the abyss I summon thee!
Instancecontenttextdata_7802_Text: Insatiable hunger of the void!Devour all light and return this world to perfect darkness!
Instancecontenttextdata_7803_Text: By Zodiark's name I command thee!River of time, mire mine enemy in thy sluggish flow!
Instancecontenttextdata_7804_Text: You shall wither in the merciless embrace of eternity!
Instancecontenttextdata_7805_Text: But...you are shorn of Her blessing!How do you yet resist me!?
